     ("We — the dissolved INDIVIDUAL","Zamyatin, 1924","#4fb0d0","The proto-dystopia and ancestor: the glass city that abolishes the ‘I’ into a scheduled ‘We,’ and cures the soul with surgery."),
     ("The Handmaid's Tale — the conscripted BODY","Atwood, 1985","#b5202a","Theocratic patriarchy after a fertility collapse: women reduced to wombs — and every horror drawn from real history."),
